1->Generate Bars
Click “Shuffle” to create a new random array of bars.

2->Choose Algorithm
Select one of the algorithms — Insertion, Selection, Bubble, or Merge Sort.

3->Watch the Animation
The bars move according to the sorting logic, visualizing each step of the algorithm.

4->Speed Control
Adjust the speed slider (1 = slow motion, 100 = very fast).

Installation & Usage:
1->Clone or Download the Project
2->Install Python
Make sure you have Python 3.8+ installed.
3->Run the Project
No extra libraries are needed (only Tkinter, which comes pre-installed with Python).
